      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FLAMING VALORA (2) stalked the lead from a middle draw and boxed on well to finish 3.5 lengths back in second (25.88) at this track in a Grade 6/MDN over 457m. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in two starts. Sure to be about the mark. BIG GRIN (7) was below best last time but prior to that was narrowly beaten when fourth (25.89) in a Grade 6 at this track. Can find the frame this time. DODGEM DUKE (4) sat on speed and lifted strongly to open winning account two back, then finished a 6 length third last start at this track over 457m (25.91). Back to track where he won his maiden. Rates a leading chance again.",
